        </div>
        <div class="sec-dms__info-options">
          <h3>Варианты<br />обследований:</h3>
          <div class="sec-dms__info-options-gender">
            <div class="sec-dms__info-options-gender-left">
              <p>Для женщин:</p>
              <div class="sec-dms__info-options-gender-list">
